data.description: Enter into open, airy great room with/tons of built-in shelves, & retro built-in planter defining the space. Unique feature can be re-purposed as seating or storage. Dining area has sunny view of inviting pool & private yard. Fully-equipped, tiled kitchen has ample cabinets, opens into breakfast room w/ two closets. Breakfast area flows into bonus room w/wood burning fireplace. Master has en suite bath w/tiled shower. Large private yard w/ deep in ground pool, unlike most pools of today. Plenty of parking for all your cars and toys in carport & double driveway. Wonderful location minutes to downtown, San Marco, Mandarin, yet tucked away near quiet parks
